@dior is heading to Dublin.
Jonathan Anderson has announced the House’s first-ever runway show in Ireland, with the Fall 2027 collection set to be unveiled at Trinity College Dublin on 4 December 2026. It’s also the designer’s first presentation on home soil since taking the creative reins at Dior.
