@louisvuitton just made the great outdoors extremely posh. Pharrell’s Fall 2027 Men’s Capsule imagines a weekend in the English countryside, bringing dandy elegance to reversible Monogram workwear, mink gilets, gingham sneakers, and heavy-duty ranger boots.⁠
⁠
Even the luggage has gone country, with olive jacquard travel bags and a basket-woven Picnic Keepall finished with an apple-shaped ID tag. The collection arrives this September.⁠

