@yohjiyamamotoofficial private drawings are going public for the first time. *"Yohji Yamamoto Drawings" collects never-before-published works selected by the designer himself, offering rare access to the creative process behind his radical fashion.⁠
⁠
Featuring flaming coats, slumped figures, and elegant dresses sketched across everything from fine paper to old newspapers, the book reveals a side of Yamamoto’s work few have ever seen.⁠

